 and exception contents.\n- `ruff` and `mypy` checks pass cleanly for the new files.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [x] None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\n- The implementation of the dispatch function effectively closes the routing gap in the asset bus.\n- Mandatory hardening checks for startup identity were verified via `tests/test_first_boot.py` and `tests/test_governor_integration.py`, which pass and confirm that `bootstrap_identity()` is correctly wired and identity persists across boots.\n- All tests for the dispatch module pass (7 passed).\n"}}
